SetTimeout & Chill License

You are free to:
- Use this code to sort your numbers… slowly.
- Show it off to friends and confuse them with asynchronous magic.
- Adjust accuracyAndDurationAmplifier to whatever number makes your timers feel appreciated.

You may not:
- Blame me if your coffee gets cold waiting for tiny numbers to sort.
- Complain that this isn’t the fastest sorting algorithm in the universe.

By using this code, you agree to:
- Smile when a number finally appears in the right place.
- Accept that programming sometimes involves waiting… and waiting…
